Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clarifies all reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and causes alibi tricks to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the midst of a slightly strange coldness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a fiery map will light the way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Red Horse within the Flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Case Part!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that was when I told that lady to back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "Give it up already, you don't even have a chance of winning."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's all really thanks to Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was able to decipher the message Heiji sent him and came to our rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, well, there's no point in talking about it. What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting that aside, Uncle... isn't your glass empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she really was a horrible woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even tried to burn us to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burn you to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she intended to set her house on fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then testify in court that we caused it because we had a grudge against her, but couldn't escape in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sure was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, someone could've assumed that it was the work of the arsonist that's been disturbing the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arsonist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the beginning of this year, there's been a number of serial arson cases in the metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say "serial", do you mean that the same method is used in each incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's no similarity in how the fires are started, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's something that's always left behind at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A figurine of a red horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. It matches the police's codename for arsonists,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Red Horse."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The arsonist must be doing this to mock the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably saying something like "I'm the arsonist. If you think you can catch me, then go ahead and try."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose the fact that no one died in the three cases can be called a blessing in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, are those three cases related somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears that the three cases are completely unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fires were scattered all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, the first one was on the 1st block of Rizen-chou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:53.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: -Chou roughly translates to "Town."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the second was on the 2nd block of Toriya-chou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the third was on the 3rd block of Okuho-chou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the next one should be at the 4th block somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Since it's possible the arsonist is setting these fires randomly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the police are keeping watch on all 4th blocks in the metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there are a lot of 4th blocks, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I know of a place that they might target, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, Kusakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked me to do him a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to investigate a suspicious person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was seen in the middle of the night on the 4th block of Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really have anywhere to go this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't Uncle, this brat, and I pay a visit to the client's house tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking Dad is okay, but you can't take Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A FIELD TRIP!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might be able to find a lead to this serial arson case, and you intend to go on a carefree field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a kid after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about the weather? It's still raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, because we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This teruterubozu always granted nice weather for Shin'ichi's important soccer games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: A teruterubozu is a paper doll to which children pray for good weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're making me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, the rain would be bad for the parents too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, tomorrow will definitely be sunny, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd,.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should have been a 100% possibility of it being sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your wish on the doll didn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because it wasn't for Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's silly, that can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we hung it up last night, it was facing outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well... It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weather all depends on Mother Nature's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look like Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s teruterubozu is starting to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, that was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... Sooner or later, you'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to go shopping for a bit, then head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji and Uncle, good luck with your detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, seriously, those two get along really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, are you jealous of Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where is this place, and when do we need to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, at the Morozumi residence on the 4th block of Haido City by 4:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Uncle's detective agency isn't on the 4th block.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, found it. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're thirty minutes late. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares, it's only 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} warned me not to be late since the client is very particular about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please leave already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to pressure you into buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:46.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to show you our antiques catalog, which has valuables such as scrolls and vases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And haven't I said this already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in those dusty pieces of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'll just leave the catalog with you, along with this good luck charm key holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you ever change your mind, please come to our store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not desperate enough to depend on such superstitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you people here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the detectives who come on behalf of Kusakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... isn't this different from what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was held captive for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have been troubled to the point that she needed the help of a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying it's just her imagination is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady's definitely hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, just like you told me, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:16.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ceramics look good on all sides, so it's best to put one at the front entrance of your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,to bring good luck and prosperity to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's just a Feng Shui teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can I help you with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, no... Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, that lady is wearing some heavy makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to come anymore, Nee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get angry, Ryoko. It just hasn't been my month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let me borrow ten thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no... Five thousand yen from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the fortune-teller! If you have bad luck, then do something about it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she's a fortune-teller...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, it's been over two hours since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen by just waiting around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that Feng Shui teacher went in and hasn't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go see what's going on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's searching for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you search for it, it's not there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video tape that I recorded of us is hidden somewhere in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:11:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an added insurance that you'll divorce your wife and be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my husband will be coming home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you guys went drinking as college friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, please relax on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't understand adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're probably separated from your wife forever, but it's scary that someone could be worse off than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the man from earlier this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably couldn't reach his daily sales quota, so he's working overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like her husband's finally coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, darling! Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Morozumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Soga, you're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go to the restroom first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you warm up the engine for me while you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't. You should walk if you're going to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't you join us for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's okay, since I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also a soccer game I want to see in the middle of the night, so I should get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, although I was curious about the conversation the two men were having...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you planning on following them? Hurry up and come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we got that call from Ran, we had no choice but to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We prepared dinner for all of us, but it's gotten cold already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the client, Morozumi san's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You said you were coming back because you were done with all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were, but some fire trucks passed us on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got worried, so we went back, and found out that it was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morozumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like the wife didn't make it out in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! If only we'd stayed here, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two went out drinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been an hour since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they came back so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they had a hunch that something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, Mama, I told you that was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the red horse that causes fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, how do you know about the red horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that, and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying! But I only saw its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it when I was watching Kamen Yaiba on the TV in our living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as Yaiba's opening theme started,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden, it got really bright outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shadow of a horse this big was projected on the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your house is next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a house to the left and right of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a red horse figurine in front of the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a red horse figurine in front of the window
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the kid was watching TV in this room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow was projected onto this curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamen Yaiba starts at 7:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that the outside lit up and caused the shadow to be projected during the opening means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that the arsonist put the horse there and set the house on fire before 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Or he at least had to have been standing by the window to put the figurine there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it was the horse that lit the fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two hours later, the fire that stole the life of Morozumi Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was finally put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you let us go inside for just a second, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't, we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could you at least tell us where the fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a request from you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, no is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Aren't fires outside of your jurisdiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fiery old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How dare you call your former supervisor a "fiery old man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Former supervisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Inspector Yuminaga from the Arson Department, First Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you part of the Homicide department?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a short period where I was in Arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you constantly caused me trouble back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You always thought every fire was arson and disturbed the scene with your sloppy investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even count the number of times the fire department complained to me about your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, weren't you like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this fire is undoubtedly arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:17:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red horse figurine was found at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After examining it in a lab, it matches perfectly with the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Yuminaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't someone be imitating the crime based on facts that newspapers have reported on the red horse or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot. No one can make an identical figure just by looking at the photos from newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those horses are made of plastic using the exact same mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, they aren't being sold anywhere, so the arsonist probably made them by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's probably having fun doing this to mock us, but now someone's died from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've gone too far this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where did it start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's this kid, your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire started in a small room in the back of the house, towards the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was also the room where they put the red horse on the windowsill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traces of kerosene on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, they probably stood outside and poured that in through the open window and lit the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, we found many strange shoe prints just outside the window by the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get some clues if we investigate them thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Your footsteps are among them too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, we're here because the fire victim, Morozumi Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, asked for our assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted us to investigate this stranger that had been lurking around her house at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, then that lady tried to convince us that it was only her imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded kind of fishy, so we stayed here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, a strange Feng Shui teacher came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought something might be wrong, so we peeked through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and found out something bad was happening inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something bad was happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man was having an affair with Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and was searching for the videotape which proves it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I think what you guys did seems more questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you'll have to let us take your shoe prints later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't be suspecting us, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot. It's obviously so we can separate your prints from the arsonist's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, was that man the only one who stopped by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Altogether, there were four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man having the affair, along with Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,her elder sister, who appears to be a fortune-teller,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a man who was selling antiques through a catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we know that neither the Feng Shui teacher nor Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s husband can be the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the neighbor's son, it was 7:30 PM when the red horse appeared by the storage window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for the teacher or the husband to have put it there, because they went drinking together around 7:20 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... We stayed here for five minutes afterwards so we could decide if we wanted to follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't see any fire or smoke then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What bothers me is why they came home so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that. A neighbor called the husband's cell phone and let him know about the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the suspicious ones are the fortune-teller and the man who was peddling antiques.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of fortune-telling, there's a fortune-teller convention going on by Haido Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then she could be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Ryoko died!? Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:21:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even warned her to be careful, since all her signs pointed toward an impending fire disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father's funeral isn't even over yet. Why is everyone leaving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Sorry to bother you, but where were you around 7:30 PM tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been here the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. Our contracts state that we have to start our shift at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one left is the man who brought the catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what that guy looked like at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, he's in his forties, about 150 cm tall, wearing round glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's probably an antique dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that he was delivering catalogs by foot means his store is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuminaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you have any idea who he might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the four red horses that were left at the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is this one charred so much more than the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rabbit?
